2026-04-30T13:58:58.8318218Z               "id": "70665e55fae49d486249c4ea2129b6fd6a9c7c02",
2026-04-30T13:58:58.8321822Z               "message": "Add Swagger/OpenAPI endpoint to Ednsv.Web\n\nAdds Swashbuckle.AspNetCore so the API surface is browsable at /swagger\nand the OpenAPI 3.0 spec is served at /swagger/v1/swagger.json. The\ndocs sit behind the existing auth middleware, so they require login\nwhen EDNSV_AUTH_TOKEN_HASH is set and are open otherwise. Endpoints\nare tagged (Validation, Cache, Config, Auth, Meta) for grouping in\nthe UI, and a *** scheme lets the \"Authorize\" button work\nagainst the AuthService-issued tokens.\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_015jVmPv4nzgdGnbXkeQiHy7",
2026-04-30T13:58:58.8325483Z               "timestamp": "2026-04-30T13:41:35Z",
