2026-04-30T13:58:58.8346769Z               "message": "Add 'API docs' link to top nav on all pages\n\nSurfaces the Swagger UI from the validator, config, and tokens pages.\nOpens in a new tab since it's a self-contained SPA distinct from the\nrest of the UI.\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_015jVmPv4nzgdGnbXkeQiHy7",
